<plot>A college senior confronts having to fight in the Vietnam War. He and his roommates start setting paper airplanes on fire and launching them from a precarious rooftop. After an intense, frenzied evening, a final decision propels him into an uncertain, potentially lethal, future. Flight raises questions that resonate again in a world immersed in strife and war.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?197729</url></doc>
